tus and translation\u003C/change>\n            \t   \u003Cchange when=\"2020-10-05\" who=\"#SS\">Simona Stoyanova normalised Unicode\u003C/change>\n            \t   \u003Cchange when=\"2020-10-08\" who=\"#SS\">Simona Stoyanova updated list of languages\u003C/change>\n            \t\u003Cchange when=\"2020-11-20\" who=\"#SS\">Simona Stoyanova added EDCS numbers\u003C/change>\n\t\t\u003Cchange when=\"2020-11-26\" who=\"#SS\">Simona Stoyanova restructured bibliography\u003C/change>\n\t    \u003Cchange when=\"2020-12-17\" who=\"#JP\">Updated Zenodo DOI\u003C/change>\n            \t\u003Cchange when=\"2021-01-19\" who=\"#SS\">renumbered files, uris and references\u003C/change>\n\t\u003C/listChange>\n        \u003C/revisionDesc>\n    \u003C/teiHeader>\n    \u003Cfacsimile>\u003Csurface/>\u003C!-- \n        \u003Csurface type=\"front\">\n            \u003Cgraphic n=\"screen\" url=\"ISic000115_tiled.tif\" height=\"3680px\" width=\"5520px\">\n                \u003Cdesc>I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana\u003C/desc>\n            \u003C/graphic>\n            \u003Cgraphic n=\"print\" url=\"ISic000115.jpg\" height=\"3680px\" width=\"5520px\">\n                \u003Cdesc>I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana\u003C/desc>\n            \u003C/graphic>\n         \u003C/surface> -->\n    \u003C/facsimile>\n    \u003Ctext>\n        \u003Cbody>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"edition\" subtype=\"primary\" xml:space=\"preserve\" xml:lang=\"la\" resp=\"#TA\">\n                \u003Cab>\n                    \u003Clb n=\"1\"/>Dis \u003Cg ref=\"#interpunct\">·\u003C/g> Manibus \u003Cg ref=\"#interpunct\">·\u003C/g> \u003Cexpan>\u003Cabbr>sac\u003C/abbr>\u003Cex>rum\u003C/ex>\u003C/expan>\n                    \u003Clb n=\"2\"/>Callis\u003Cchoice>\u003Ccorr>t\u003C/corr>\u003Csic>i\u003C/sic>\u003C/choice>o \u003Cg ref=\"#interpunct\">·\u003C/g> \u003Cchoice>\u003Ccorr>t\u003C/corr>\u003Csic>i\u003C/sic>\u003C/choice>raeci \u003Cg ref=\"#interpunct\">·\u003C/g> \u003Cexpan>\u003Cabbr>Treb\u003C/abbr>\u003Cex cert=\"low\">oni\u003C/ex>\u003C/expan> \u003Cg ref=\"#interpunct\">·\u003C/g>\n                    \u003Clb n=\"3\"/>fecit \u003Cg ref=\"#interpunct\">·\u003C/g> Spec\u003Csupplied reason=\"omitted\" cert=\"low\">i\u003C/supplied> \u003Cg ref=\"#interpunct\">·\u003C/g> eques\n                    \u003Clb n=\"4\"/>\u003Cexpan>\u003Cabbr>cons\u003C/abbr>\u003Cex>ervo\u003C/ex>\u003C/expan> \u003Cg ref=\"#interpunct\">·\u003C/g> bene merenti\n                    \u003Clb n=\"5\"/>\u003Cexpan>\u003Cabbr>v\u003C/abbr>\u003Cex cert=\"low\">ixit\u003C/ex>\u003C/expan> \u003Cg ref=\"#interpunct\">·\u003C/g> \u003Cnum value=\"20\">XX\u003C/num>\n                \u003C/ab>\n            \u003C/div>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"apparatus\">\n                \u003ClistApp>\n                    \u003Capp>\u003Cnote>Text based on ILTermini\u003C/note>\u003C/app>\n                    \u003Capp loc=\"Line1\">\u003Cnote>Gualtherus: CALLISIO·IRAECI\u003C/note>\u003C/app>\n                \u003C/listApp>\n            \u003C/div>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"translation\" xml:lang=\"en\" resp=\"#TA\">\n                \u003Cp>Sacred to the Shades of the Underworld; to Callistus, a thraex (of Trebonius?). Spec(i?)es, an eques, made (this) to his well-deserving fellow-slave, who lived 20 years (?).\u003C/p>\n            \u003C/div>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"commentary\">\n                \u003Cp>\u003C!--commented out pending revision-->\n                    \u003C!--Possibly commemorating a gladiator (but this does seem a little tenuous! apparently erected by another slave, called ?Speces?)-->\n                    \u003C!--Tuuli: Probably both gladiators, if we take thraex to be the gladiatorial type rather than an ethnicising name? Equites, gladiators \n                        who rode to fight in horseback, apparently often opened gladiatorial games and were popular during the imperial era.\n                        Mommsen and Bivona prefer to expand the last 'v' as v(icit) (Bivona v(icit?), Mommsen: v(icit vicies?)), so that the last line \n                        records Callistus´ victories, but I have for now put in Manganaro's more boring but perhaps more probable interpretation that \n                        it signifies the years lived. -->\u003C/p>\n            \u003C/div>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"bibliography\">\n                \u003ClistBibl type=\"edition\">\n                    \u003Cbibl>\n                        \u003Cauthor>Gualtherus\u003C/author>\n                        \u003Cdate>1624\u003C/date>\n                        \u003CcitedRange>124\u003C/citedRange>\n                        \u003Cptr target=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/GIN6NANU\"/>\n                        \u003Cref target=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002388\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002388\u003C/ref>\n                    \u003C/bibl>\n                    \u003Cbibl>\n                        \u003Cauthor>Gualtherus\u003C/author>\n                        \u003Cdate>1624 [1625]\u003C/date>\n                        \u003CcitedRange>287\u003C/citedRange>\n                        \u003Cptr target=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/ZP8DE8KS\"/>\n                        \u003Cref target=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001931\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001931\u003C/ref>\n                    \u003C/bibl>\n                    \u003Cbibl type=\"corpus\" n=\"CIL\">\n                        \u003Cauthor>Mommsen\u003C/author>\n                        \u003Cdate>1883\u003C/date>\n                        \u003CcitedRange>\n                            \u003Cref target=\"http://arachne.uni-koeln.de/item/buchseite/650797\">7364\u003C/ref>\n                        \u003C/citedRange>\n                        \u003Cptr target=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/GQN8UZSI\"/>\n                    \u003Cref target=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000589\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000589\u003C/ref>\u003C/bibl>\n                    \u003Cbibl type=\"corpus\" n=\"ILMusTermini\">\n                         \u003Cauthor>Bivona\u003C/author>\n                         \u003Cdate>1994\u003C/date> \n                        \u003CcitedRange>33\u003C/citedRange>\n                        \u003Cptr target=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/JCV85C79\"/>\n                    \u003Cref target=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002137\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002137\u003C/ref>\u003C/bibl>\n                    \u003Cbibl type=\"corpus\" n=\"ILS\">\n                        \u003CcitedRange>5093\u003C/citedRange>\n                        \u003Cptr target=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/XHMS9K6S\"/>\n                    \u003Cref target=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000352\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000352\u003C/ref>\u003C/bibl>\n                    \u003Cbibl>\n                        \u003Cauthor>Rizzo\u003C/author>\n                        \u003Cdate>1989\u003C/date>\n                        \u003CcitedRange>106 no.111\u003C/citedRange>\n                        \u003Cptr target=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/K83EWCEC\"/>\n                    \u003Cref target=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001640\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001640\u003C/ref>\u003C/bibl>\n                    \u003Cbibl>\n                        \u003Cauthor>Manganaro\u003C/author>\n                        \u003Cdate>1988\u003C/date>\n                        \u003CcitedRange>57\u003C/citedRange>\n                        \u003Cptr target=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/RZSFKACR\"/>\n                    \u003Cref target=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001427\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001427\u003C/ref>\u003C/bibl>\n                \u003C/listBibl>\n\t   \u003ClistBibl type=\"discussion\">\u003Cbibl/>\u003C/listBibl>\n            \u003C/div>\n        \u003C/body>\n    \u003C/text>\n\u003C/TEI>\n"],"uses":{"params":["slug"]}}]}
